title: TUESDAY 3/16 - Let the frenzy begin!
itunes:title: TUESDAY 3/16 - Let the frenzy begin!
description:
Free agency frenzy is underway and we have an update on all the latest moves from around the league including the Super Bowl Champion Buccaneers (1:01). The Patriots (0:28) were very busy on Monday bringing in reinforcements for Bill Belichick, and the Saints (2:18) bringing back the possible successor to Drew Brees
